Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要…填写现实世界的情报啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的多谢你处处帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦 反正乘坐「沙漠赛车」也挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(708,670)}Buggy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 你比赛的区域是哪一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…F区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F区37号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是同时报名的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是F区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12号的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 就算碰上了也已经是决赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了是指什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能进到淘汰制预赛的决赛阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论最后输赢 都可以获得正赛参赛资格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 我们一起晋级正赛不是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 如果真的在决赛碰上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会因为是预赛 而放水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 碰上了的话就让我们尽全力比试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:15.41,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H414285&\bord0}第三届 预赛淘汰赛报名 已经全部结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 以国外的游戏来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这游戏的日语支持做的还真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明官网就只有英文而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然运营方「ZASKAR」是美国企业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在这个日本服务器的运营人员中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也有日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你也知道 GGO不管在日本还是美国的法律上都属于灰色地带了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为通货还原系统吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对外的主页上 都只有最低限度的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如角色管理 通货还原所用到的电子钱包账户之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与游戏相关的手续多数都只能在游戏中办理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢…好厉害的游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 与现实世界几乎完全隔绝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也因为这 游戏中的和现实中的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直判若两人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…没什么 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多得去预赛会场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里 就在这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去更衣室吧 你也得先换上刚才买的战斗服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.04,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H62655F&\frz353.8\pos(839,160)}BoB3的准备时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.04,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H62655F&\pos(821,394)\frz355.1}还剩余28分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都是群乱来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？乱来的家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那些吓人的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在开赛前30分钟就在那秀主要装备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就像在说「请来针对我吧」一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是 光剑和「FN.5-7」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自己的比赛开始之前再装备比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢 你也得赶紧换装了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…那个…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都没有做自我介绍…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有意思的名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男性？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？什么？但是你明明…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 男人？！就你那个造型？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是…接下来要怎么做我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我没什么认识的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.50,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H62655F&\frz353.8\pos(839,160)}BoB3的准备时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.53,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H62655F&\pos(821,394)\frz355.1}还剩余10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.29,0:08:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只跟你讲最基本的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我们就是对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会了 我并没有原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒计时为0时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:59.16,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H2B2B2B&\bord2\3c&HD4C89A&}剩余{\c&H0000FF&}09{\c&H2B2B2B&}分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的所有参赛者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将会与预赛第一场的对手将会被自动传送到专属的某个赛场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛场是1000m3的正方体空间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地形 气候 时间都是随机的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双方将在至少距离500m的地方开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决出胜负后 胜者回到这个待机区域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,败者将会被传送到一楼大厅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便输掉也不会随机掉武装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为F区有64人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢五次就能晋级决赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到正式比赛的出赛权
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就解释这么多 别问我问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打到决赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都教了你那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一点也想要教给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你尝尝败北子弹的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就期待一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果预赛都过不了我也别玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把高手全都杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计今天是我们最后一次谈话了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就报备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是将要打败你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:28.74,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(687,99)}诗音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是桐人 多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呦 诗音 怎么这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还担心你会不会迟到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 「镜子」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs33\pos(688,670)}Spiegel
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到点闲事占据了时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你不是不参赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道碍不碍事 我是来给你加油打气的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里能看到大屏幕的实况转播
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 闲事是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把对面那家伙带来这里之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我就是对面那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你好 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是诗音的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别被外表骗了 那家伙是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫桐人 性别男
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男的？！就是说…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗音真的很照顾我 各方面…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪里照顾你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我不记得同意你叫我诗音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么冷淡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么冷不冷淡的 我根本不认识你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都帮人家选装备了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始第三届Bullet of Bullets预赛淘汰赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加比赛的各位玩家将在倒计时结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自动传送到预赛第一场的比赛场地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝给位好运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打到决赛 听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会轰飞你脑袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你都约我了 我怎么能不赴约呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有点玩过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.47,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H5E5954&\fad(400,0)\frx354\fry14\pos(469,297)\frz345.3}准备时间：剩余        秒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.47,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H5E5954&\fad(400,0)\pos(428,446)\frz347\frx342\fry10\org(430.415,420.8)}赛场：古代寺院遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀掉所有高手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩会不会是死枪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟…哪一个才是真正的诗音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里想破头也不会有结果的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在剑上过招的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 如果交火的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会得出什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:43.68,Extra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\frz347.6\pos(803,292)\c&H393A37&}剩余 {\c&H2D1FD9&}01 {\c&H393A37&}秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么打根本靠不过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能靠这把剑防住几枪的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要弹开这种速度的子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须精确地预测子弹的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,着弹线会准确地告诉我子弹的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.87,Warning,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}(｀・ω・´)外挂模式开启(｀・ω・´)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没搞错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离这么近的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…又犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这要人命的战斗还要再打4场…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗音她在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…真货吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真货…？什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了…你比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用了…剑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是又怎么 又不违反比赛规则
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再问 一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…真货吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 认识我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有错 我肯定在哪见过这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也像这样面对面说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在哪里…我到底在哪里和这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个名字…那种剑技…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…真货吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…我也认识这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙跟我一样也是SAO生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁…到底在哪见过…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 旷野的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
